a fine"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for, sometimes,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoramN","text_ar":"مَغْرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AilotizaAmu guromK","text_ar":"اِلْتِزَامُ غُرْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd in lii. 40. [See also 5, and 8.]) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garimotu Eanohu maA lazimahu mina","text_ar":"غَرِمْتُ عَنْهُ مَا لَزِمَهُ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~iyapi","text_ar":"الدِّيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I paid for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his stead, what was obligatory upon him, of the bloodwit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eql","text_ar":"عقل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garima fiY tijaAratihi","text_ar":"غَرِمَ فِى تِجَارَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suffered loss, in his traffic; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasira","text_ar":"خَسِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiHa","text_ar":"رَبِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurima A^anofFA","text_ar":"غُرِمَ اَنْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rugima","text_ar":"رُغِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from which it is app. formed by transposition]."}],"source_refs":["JK","S","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}